<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .profile-section {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .profile-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .profile-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #667eea;
        }
        .value {
            color: #333;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background-color: #667eea;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        h3 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        li {
            padding: 8px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🎉 Welcome to SkillBridge!</h1>
            <p>Your tutor profile has been approved</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello <%= userName %>,</h2>
            
            <p>Congratulations! Your tutor profile has been successfully approved and is now active on SkillBridge.</p>
            
            <h3>Your Tutor Profile Details:</h3>
            <div class="profile-section">
                <div class="profile-item">
                    <span class="label">Email:</span>
                    <span class="value"><%= userEmail %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="profile-item">
                    <span class="label">Bio:</span>
                    <span class="value"><%= bio %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="profile-item">
                    <span class="label">Hourly Rate:</span>
                    <span class="value">$<%= hourlyRate %>/hour</span>
                </div>
                <div class="profile-item">
                    <span class="label">Experience:</span>
                    <span class="value"><%= experienceYrs %> years</span>
                </div>
                <div class="profile-item">
                    <span class="label">Location:</span>
                    <span class="value"><%= location || 'Not specified' %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="profile-item">
                    <span class="label">Languages:</span>
                    <span class="value"><%= languages || 'Not specified' %></span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3>🚀 Next Steps:</h3>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Complete Your Categories:</strong> Add the subjects you're specialized in teaching</li>
                <li><strong>Set Your Availability:</strong> Define your working hours and available time slots</li>
                <li><strong>Prepare for Bookings:</strong> Start accepting student bookings and earn money</li>
            </ol>

            <h3>📌 Important Information:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Your profile is now visible to students on SkillBridge</li>
                <li>You will receive notifications when students request bookings</li>
                <li>Payment processing begins once students book your sessions</li>
                <li>Maintain a high rating to attract more students</li>
            </ul>

            <p style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" class="button">Go to Your Tutor Dashboard</a>
            </p>

            <h3>Need Help?</h3>
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our support team at <strong>support@skillbridge.com</strong> or reply to this email.</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Happy teaching!<br/><strong>Team SkillBridge</strong></p>

            <div class="footer">
                <p>© 2026 SkillBridge. All rights reserved.<br/>
                This is an automated message, please do not reply directly.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
